{"tid":1113939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為外判程序員突倒地惹加班累死疑雲 官方：低血糖導致","createTime":"2019-04-18T08:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T20:00:26.000Z","uid":75969,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cbcd7568e686a119ede0df1cb4d4ec2301302582","tid":1113939,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T08:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190418/_2019041810540892210.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190418%2F_2019041810540892210.jpg&h=e6bd1397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，一段「程序員猝死」的閉路電視片段突然在微博上流傳，引起了網民廣泛關注，引發新一輪的996工作制討論，<span style=\"color: red;\">所謂的996就是早上9點返工，晚上9點下班，每周工作6天</span>，這就是所謂的「996」工作制。周三（17日）該程序員所在公司中軟國際回應稱：<span style=\"color: red;\">該員工是因為低血糖而暈倒，已回復正常上班。</span>據了解，中軟是華為的外判公司，曾有員工抱怨「加班多」。公司回應稱是根據項目進度加班，並沒有硬性要求996。<br />\n<br />\n從影片所見，一名員工在某公司的辦公室摸着肚子扶牆站立，突然無法站穩，直挺挺90度的摔倒在在地，然後再身體抽搐了幾下，身邊的同事緊急前往扶起救助。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛為這位倒下的員工祈福。周三（17日），有國內媒體聯繫到了該員工所在的公司「中軟國際」。<br />\n<br />\n中軟國際回應稱，該員工是其南京分公司的員工，職位是程序員，影片中暈倒的原因是他沒有吃早餐，引起的低血糖暈倒，該員工本身就有低血糖，當天暈倒後，同事已經將其送到了醫院，醫院也出具了低血糖的診斷報告，該員工當天就已經出院，現已恢復上班。<br />\n<br />\n此外，中軟國際否認了「996」或加班情況導致暈倒的傳言，表示其工作時間是正常的。<br />\n<br />\n中軟國際是華為三大外判公司之一，是國內大型綜合性軟件與信息服務企業，主營業務是軟件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/982336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F982336&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSFhCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=3ac3c032\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F982336&h=7c3907d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/982336</a><br />\n<br />\n可以返工是福氣 最愛返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a6305d5966e2e85d1a933f7889bb0824161b61","tid":1113939,"uid":582,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"996就頂唔順，有冇渣成咁呀"},{"pid":"ae37b938e1f7cdbc27d232ab2843ddc90106c913","tid":1113939,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68a6305d5966e2e85d1a933f7889bb0824161b61","tid":1113939,"uid":582,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"996就頂唔順，有冇渣成咁呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"鬼叫支那狗個底差<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73787fc6ef4448a7c6d5e90994b7cf1cf768657d","tid":1113939,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T08:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6de971cd8bd66dba6f3636161ebf1709f72603","tid":1113939,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"@奶波呢?"},{"pid":"89f7ac75f43ad095e62c9402188cc51c98278af8","tid":1113939,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e6de971cd8bd66dba6f3636161ebf1709f72603","tid":1113939,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"@奶波呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T17:03:34.000Z","msg":"@老貓呢？"},{"pid":"cda40cc834c1f1e1a9e5aef81c7907305ebd91ed","tid":1113939,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"中軟呢個名唔好意頭"},{"pid":"153c82937cea0866bf4833df750c251b34d3d9e0","tid":1113939,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T20:00:26.000Z","msg":"支那人出事唔係低血糖就高血壓㗎啦 , 再唔係既抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}